<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.2.8">
<l>paṉṉiru tiṅkaḷ vayiṟṟil koṇṭavap pāṅkiṉāl</l>
<l>eṉiḷaṅ koṅkai yamutamūṭ ṭiyeṭut tuyāṉ</l>
<l>poṉṉaṭi nōvap pulariyē kāṉilkaṉ ṟiṉpiṉ</l>
<l>eṉṉiḷañ ciṅkattaip pōkkiṉē ṉellēpā vamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Just as he was kept in the womb for 12 months,</l>
<l>I have raised [him] and fed [him] the nectar of my young breasts,</l>
<l>I sent my young lion after the calves in the forest at dawn</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [now his] golden feet ache.</l>
<l>Alas! What a sin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
